channel.title: Lists. (Ores, Trees etc)
channel.description:
Hi there,
I am looking for [b]your[/b] help!
I am trying to assemble accurate lists of trees, mining rocks, fishing spots(With location X and Y), Ranges/Cooking spots, Thieving stalls and Forges. For a 377 server.
This is not an easy task as most object lists are actually missing a few objects and for things like mining rocks they don't actually tell you what type of ore it is for.
I have already done the list of Mining Rocks (I think) and I shall paste it here as an example of the format I would like:
[code=java] case 2108://Clay case 2109: case 10949: case 9711: case 9712: case 9713: case 11189: case 11190: case 11191: case 14904: case 14905:
case 2091://Copper case 2090: case 3042: case 9708: case 9709: case 9710: case 11936: case 11937: case 11938: case 11960: case 11961: case 11962: case 14856: case 14857: case 14858: case 14906: case 14907:
case 2094://Tin case 2095: case 3043: case 9714: case 9715: case 9716: case 11933: case 11934: case 11935: case 11957: case 11958: case 11959: case 14902: case 14903:
case 2110://Blurite case 10583: case 10584:
case 2092://Iron case 2093: case 6943: case 6944: case 9717: case 9718: case 9719: case 11954: case 11955: case 11956: case 14900: case 14901: case 14913: case 14914:
case 2100://Silver case 2101: case 6945: case 6946: case 11186: case 11187: case 11188: case 11948: case 11949: case 11950:
case 2096://Coal case 2097: case 10948: case 4676: case 11930: case 11931: case 11932: case 11963: case 11964: case 11965: case 14850: case 14851: case 14852:
case 10946://Sandstone
case 2098://Gold case 2099: case 9720: case 9721: case 9722: case 11183: case 11184: case 11185: case 11951: case 11952: case 11953:
case 2111://Gems
case 10947://Granite
case 2102://Mithril case 2103: case 11942: case 11943: case 11944: case 11945: case 11946: case 11947: case 14853: case 14854: case 14855:
case 2104://Adamant case 2105: case 11939: case 11940: case 11941: case 14862: case 14863: case 14864:
case 2106://Runite case 2107: case 14859: case 14860: case 14861:[/code]
Trees, Ranges, Thieving stalls and Forges can be done in the above format.
But as fishing spots have multiple clicking options something like this could be used instead
[code] Fishing spot Id, Fish Type1, Fish type2, Fish type3 etc [/code]
Please feel free to contribute/error check. Any contributions will be added to the post.
Also please check my mining rock list as I didn't play Runescape for quite awhile and the colours have changed on some rocks etc so I am not sure if they are right. And I am probably missing a few. :)
Thanks in advance.
